headline: Tractor Supply Recognized at National FFA Convention for Support of Agriculture Education
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 03, 2025--The energy was electric in Indianapolis last week as more than 70,000 students, teachers and agricultural leaders gathered for the 98th Annual National FFA Convention and Expo. Among them was Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), proudly celebrating four decades of partnership with the National FFA Organization — and a shared commitment to growing the next generation of agricultural leaders.
